<section class="py-6 sm:py-12 sm:px-3 lg:px-8">
  <div
    class="overflow-hidden bg-gray-900 px-6 pt-12 shadow-2xl sm:rounded-3xl sm:px-16 md:pt-16 lg:px-24 lg:pt-0"
  >
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8 items-center">
      <div class="text-center lg:text-left py-8 lg:py-16">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white sm:text-3xl">
          From The Head of the School
        </h2>
        <span class="block text-gray-300 mt-2">- Prof. Rajnish Kumar</span>
        <p class="mt-4 text-lg leading-7 text-white">
          "The School of Sustainability at IIT Madras will concentrate on three
          key areas: (I) transforming IIT Madras into a NetZero, sustainable
          campus; (II) embedding sustainability into the academic curriculum;
          and (III) unifying government and industry-funded research aligned
          with the UN Sustainable Development Goals. Through science, practical
          implementation, and policy interventions, the School aims to create a
          comprehensive impact towards achieving a NetZero India."
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="flex justify-center lg:justify-end">
        <img
          src="../../public/image/V.Kamakoti.svg"
          alt="Head V.Kamakoti "
          class="rounded-xl object-cover h-64 w-64 lg:h-80 lg:w-80"
        />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
